## Staying connected with Ping-Pong messages

To ensure that you stay connected to either the `Account` or `Trade` WebSocket you must send a "PING" message every 30 seconds on the WebSocket you wish to monitor. VALR will respond with a **PONG** event. The message must be as follows:

``` json
{
  "type": "PING"
}

 ```

On the `Trade` WebSocket the **PONG** message body will be "NO_SUBSCRIPTIONS" if you are not subscribed to any message types.

